735
01:12:10,500 --> 01:12:16,050
â™« Rather than digesting the boring days that go by,  â™«

736
01:12:16,050 --> 01:12:20,810
â™« I wanted to run away so many times, 
 I hate the state of chaos, so I pried open my head â™«

737
01:12:20,810 --> 01:12:25,740
No matter how you look at it, the correct destination.

738
01:12:27,080 --> 01:12:28,400
I'm back.

739
01:12:28,400 --> 01:12:30,460
Welcome home, dinner is ready!

740
01:12:30,460 --> 01:12:32,550
Thank you, I'll eat.

741
01:12:38,400 --> 01:12:40,800
- Do you want to drink some wine? 
 - I do!

742
01:12:40,800 --> 01:12:43,130
That looks delicious!

743
01:12:43,130 --> 01:12:45,080
Let's eat!

744
01:12:46,270 --> 01:12:49,660
That's right. This is the correct life.

745
01:12:50,540 --> 01:12:54,830
There's nothing more to think about.

746
01:12:54,830 --> 01:12:59,660
I've obtained a normal life.

747
01:13:01,200 --> 01:13:06,200
[Thirty-two]

748
01:13:10,150 --> 01:13:12,260
Just wait a moment.

749
01:13:30,490 --> 01:13:32,880
Is this seat free?

750
01:13:32,910 --> 01:13:34,880
Go ahead.

751
01:13:38,760 --> 01:13:41,930
- You're drinking alone. 
 - Yeah.

752
01:13:54,050 --> 01:13:55,700
You don't like the smoke?

753
01:13:55,700 --> 01:13:58,660
Uh, it's not that.

754
01:13:59,720 --> 01:14:03,910
The person I was with before smoked the same kind of cigarettes.

755
01:14:06,860 --> 01:14:09,040
[Peace Light]

756
01:14:20,920 --> 01:14:22,980
I'm home.

757
01:14:33,380 --> 01:14:35,180
Welcome back.

758
01:14:35,180 --> 01:14:38,130
- Would a simple dinner be all right? 
 - Yeah.

759
01:14:38,130 --> 01:14:41,390
Go change, you reek of cigarettes.

760
01:14:41,400 --> 01:14:43,040
Okay.

761
01:15:05,200 --> 01:15:08,900
Sorry! Give me a moment.

762
01:15:10,890 --> 01:15:12,810
Is this your first time?

763
01:15:12,810 --> 01:15:15,190
It's okay. I'll wait.

764
01:15:43,470 --> 01:15:44,800
Welcome.

765
01:15:44,800 --> 01:15:47,230
- Would the usual seat be okay? 
 - Yeah.

766
01:15:47,230 --> 01:15:49,550
Understood, please go on then.

